-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />
<br />
as for stacking.<br />
<br />
The sub ink parts are piles of dust.<br />
<br />
Piles of dust &quot;stack&quot; really well<br />
<br />
Vials do not stack in nearly as small a sapce as a pile of dust does.  Think of GHS as a can of sterno... again... takes up more space than a pile of dust.<br />
<br />
the saltpeter, sulfur, rock salt... though also dust... were existing items in game, and just were not changed.  At some point I may change it also, but I am not in a rush to do so, there are more important things to work on... though this could slide in becuase the change is fast.  (even simple changes like altering the stacking, and it is simple, take upwards of 30 to 60 minutes because they have to be documented and spot tested)<br />
<br />
I have said this before, but expect I will be repeating it alot.<br />
I will not change stacking JUST to make things convienient, there has to be some realism to them stacking that much.<br />
